   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The bypass mains stabilizer <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">T090</b> is a combination of
a variable auto transformer <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">T2</b>, a motor <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">M1</b>, a booster
transformer <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">T1</b> and an electronic controller <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">N1</b>.</p>
